                                                       update_bson_document                                                        
---------------------------------------------------------------------
 { "_id" : { "$numberInt" : "1" }, "matrix" : [ [ { "$numberInt" : "0" } ], [ { "$numberInt" : "1" }, { "$numberInt" : "2" } ] ] }
(1 row)

